    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1894-12-02T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1894-12-02T00:00:00-05:00" n="724" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d724">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Terrell</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Pera</hi> (<hi rend="smallcaps">Constantinople</hi>)</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-12-02">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 2,
                                1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Information from British ambassador indicates far more loss of lives in
                            Armenia attended with atrocities than stated in my telegram of 28th.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Terrell.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
